name: removeOptionalKeysFromObject

type.rawType: <TObject extends import("/Users/king/King/operations/tools/util/js-util/src/NestedPartial").O>(object: TObject, keys: Exclude<keyof T, Exclude<import("/Users/king/King/operations/tools/util/js-util/src/types").KeysOfType<T, Exclude<T[keyof T], undefined>>, undefined>>[]) => TObject

value:
<TObject extends O>(
  object: TObject,
  keys: OptionalKeys<TObject>[]
): TObject => {
  const newObject = keys.reduce((objectNow, key) => {
    return {
      ...objectNow,
      [key]: undefined,
    };
  }, object);

  return newObject;
}
